<section style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); visibility: visible;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0px 24px; line-height: 0; box-sizing: border-box; visibility: visible;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: 16px; margin-right: 16px; visibility: visible;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-aistatus="1" data-ratio="1.0324074074074074" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/4n6oYiaAFMS7YoWL5HwTVdoiaZLGPnqFzv0IngIiaQz3qgbnjpNIoEbvjkKyqlcgJCubJBFZw5I0ce50sBmSwLlvUOibeWbQdRqqV0hK4rGdark/640?wx_fmt=jpeg#imgIndex=0" data-w="1080" style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 645px !important; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-original-style="vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;" data-index="2" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/4n6oYiaAFMS7YoWL5HwTVdoiaZLGPnqFzv0IngIiaQz3qgbnjpNIoEbvjkKyqlcgJCubJBFZw5I0ce50sBmSwLlvUOibeWbQdRqqV0hK4rGdark/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1#imgIndex=0" _width="100%" alt="图片" data-report-img-idx="0" data-fail="0"></section></section><section style="line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">今天一条新闻炸了整个科技圈。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">Twitter和Square的创始人Jack Dorsey宣布，他的公司Block（就是做Cash App和Square的那家）将裁掉近一半的员工。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">从10000多人直接砍到不到6000人，超过4000人被要求离开。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">裁员原因不是公司经营不善。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">恰恰相反，Block刚刚公布的财报很亮眼：毛利润同比增长</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">24</span></span><span leaf="">%，Cash App业务增长33%，调整后每股收益超出华尔街预期。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">裁员的原因只有一个：AI。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong><span leaf="" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: normal;">Jack在致股东信中写得非常直白：</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">“智能工具已经改变了建设和运营一家公司的含义。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">一个显著更小的团队，用我们正在打造的工具，能做得更多、做得更好。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">而且智能工具的能力每周都在复合增长。”</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">消息一出，Block盘后股价暴涨超过23%。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">市场在用真金白银投票：裁掉人类员工，是利好。</span></span></strong></p></section><section style="text-align: center;margin: 24px 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-aistatus="1" data-ratio="1.5058823529411764" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/4n6oYiaAFMS5kmyN9T99nsBlT9XDBumndic95XjoLFISUmyErr7ibb9kkeCby4S3z4rLY8D57QLDibWdnFpj5B8FNSVoxKFK0ZwVOqHQz4DDiaIQ/640?wx_fmt=png#imgIndex=1" data-w="850" style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 676.997px !important; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-original-style="vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;" data-index="3" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/4n6oYiaAFMS5kmyN9T99nsBlT9XDBumndic95XjoLFISUmyErr7ibb9kkeCby4S3z4rLY8D57QLDibWdnFpj5B8FNSVoxKFK0ZwVOqHQz4DDiaIQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1#imgIndex=1" _width="100%" alt="图片" data-report-img-idx="1" data-fail="0"></section></section><section style="font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">| Jack Dorsey发帖原文</span></p></section><section style="margin: 32px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center;font-size: 28px;color: rgb(255, 129, 36);font-family: PingFangSC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: left;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">01&nbsp;</span></strong></p></section></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 32px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 20px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: PingFangSC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="font-size: 25px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 20px;background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">这件事的来龙去脉</span></span></strong></p></section></section><section style="line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">这不是Block第一次调整人员。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">过去两年，公司一直在通过绩效考核逐步精简团队，同时大力投入AI工具，包括自研的AI编程工具Goose。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">但这次不同，这次是一刀切。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">Jack说他面临两个选择：</span></span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">在未来几个月甚至几年里慢慢裁，还是现在一次性做到位。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">他选了后者。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">他的原话是：</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">“反复多轮裁员会摧毁士气、分散注意力，也会动摇客户和股东对我们领导力的信任。”</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">对被裁的员工，Block给出了相当体面的补偿方案：</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">20周薪资加上每年工龄额外1周，股权归属到5月底，6个月医疗保险，保留公司设备，外加5000美元过渡补贴。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">但Jack真正让人震动的是这句话：</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">“</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">我认为在未来一年内，大多数公司都会得出同样的结论，做出类似的结构性调整。</span></span></strong><span leaf="">我宁愿诚实地、按我们自己的节奏走到那里，而不是被动地被迫应对。”</span></p></section><section style="margin: 32px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center;font-size: 28px;color: rgb(255, 129, 36);font-family: PingFangSC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: left;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">02</span></strong></p></section></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 32px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 20px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: PingFangSC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">Dorsey 发言里最重要的信号</span></span></strong></p></section></section><section style="line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">我仔细读了他在X上的长信，提炼出几个关键信息。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">第一，这不是止血，是主动进化。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">他反复强调业务在增长、利润在改善。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">盈利良好的公司主动裁掉40%员工，在历史上极其罕见。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">第二，AI不只是提效工具，而是组织结构变量。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">他说的不是“我们效率提升10%”，而是“更小更扁平的团队加上智能工具，从根本上改变了建设和运营公司的方式”。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">这是范氏级别的变化。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">第三，一次性承受痛苦，比长期消耗更健康。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">很多CEO会选择渐进式裁员，降低舆论压力。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">Jack选了最激进的方式：一步到位，然后从一个他相信的结构重新出发。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">第四，这封信不只是写给Block。</span></span></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">“大多数公司都会得出同样的结论。”这句话更像是在对整个行业喊话。</span></p></section><section style="margin: 32px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center;font-size: 28px;color: rgb(255, 129, 36);font-family: PingFangSC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: left;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">03</span></strong></p></section></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 32px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 20px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: PingFangSC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="font-size: 25px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 20px;background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">不只是Block，这个趋势在蔓延</span></span></strong></p></section></section><section style="line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">如果把时间线拉开，会看到清晰的趋势。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">去年Shopify的CEO Tobi Lütke发内部备忘录，</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">要求</span></span></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">团队在新增人手前，必须证明AI做不了这项工作。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">Pinterest裁了15%，把资源转向AI。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">Amazon今年裁掉16000个企业岗位，内部强调“更少层级”以适应AI。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">根据数据，</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">2025年美国因AI直接导致的裁员超过55000人，是两年前的12倍。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">但Block这次规模完全不同。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">不是5%、15%，而是40%。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">华尔街分析师称这是“AI叙事中的标志性时刻”。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">S&amp;P500历史上，从未有一家盈利状况良好的公司，主动裁掉近一半员工，却因此获得市场热烈掌声。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">当资本市场把裁掉人类当成利好来庆祝，一个新阶段确实已经开始。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">作为一个每天都在用AI做产品和内容的人，我对这条新闻的感受很复杂。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">一方面，我完全理解Jack的逻辑。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">我亲眼见证了AI工具过去一年的能力跃升。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">一个人加上各种AI工具，确实能完成过去一个团队的工作。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">这不是夸张，是现实。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">从这个角度看，他只是做了一个诚实的决定。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">另一方面，4000个人一夜失去工作，这不是数字，是4000个具体的人生。</span></span></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">即便补偿体面，冲击依然巨大。</span></p></section><section style="margin: 32px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center;font-size: 28px;color: rgb(255, 129, 36);font-family: PingFangSC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: left;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">04&nbsp;</span></strong></p></section></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 32px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 20px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: PingFangSC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="font-size: 25px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 20px;background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">为什么大多数公司都会走这条路？</span></span></strong></p></section></section><section style="line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">因为这是一道数学题，不是选择题。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">Block裁掉40%员工，毛利润增长24%，管理层上调全年预期，股价上涨超23%。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">资本市场给出的信号非常明确：更少的人+AI做出更好的业绩，会被奖励。</span></span></strong></p></section><section style="text-align: center;margin: 24px 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-aistatus="1" data-ratio="0.9824074074074074" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/4n6oYiaAFMS789lTJCUAicRdKOS5sJYZD138DadgSZnSzFDNzicCNcJianvywXvb1gwAPiab4O6UD2NtQFdudoohAsrQKae2szJXribkNiaceaWM6g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg#imgIndex=2" data-w="1080" style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 676.997px !important; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-original-style="vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;" data-index="4" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/4n6oYiaAFMS789lTJCUAicRdKOS5sJYZD138DadgSZnSzFDNzicCNcJianvywXvb1gwAPiab4O6UD2NtQFdudoohAsrQKae2szJXribkNiaceaWM6g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1#imgIndex=2" _width="100%" alt="图片" data-report-img-idx="2" data-fail="0"></section></section><section style="font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">| Block裁员后股价上涨22%</span></p></section><section style="margin: 24px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">当你的竞争对手这么做了，并获得更高利润率和更低成本结构，你不跟进，就会在竞争中落后。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">市场会逼你做决定。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">Jack也说：</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">“我不认为我们是先行者，我认为大多数公司已经晚了。”</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">这更像多米诺骨牌。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">第一块倒下之后，剩下的只是时间问题。</span></p></section></section><section style="margin: 32px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center;font-size: 28px;color: rgb(255, 129, 36);font-family: PingFangSC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: left;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">05</span></strong></p></section></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 32px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 20px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: PingFangSC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="font-size: 25px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 20px;background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">普通人该怎么办</span></span></strong></p></section></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 24px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">第一，现在就开始用AI工作。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">不要等公司逼你。无论你做什么行业，都开始把AI融入工作流。用它写邮件、做总结、分析数据。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">用得越早，你的不可替</span></strong></span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">代性越</span></span></strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">强。</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">第二，从执行者转向决策者。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">AI擅长执行，不擅长判断。方向选择、优先级取舍、对人的理解，这些是人类的价值所在。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">把自己的能力锚定在判断力和品味上，而不是执行速度上。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">第三，认真思考“一人公司”的能力。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">AI让一个人拥有过去一个团队的生产力。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">即便不创业，也要问自己：如果岗位消失，我是否能靠技能和AI工具养活自己？如果暂时不能，哪些能力需要提升？</span></p><span data-mpa-action-id="mm46rblg13mc"></span><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">对所有人来说，这都是提醒：</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">学习AI，靠近技术底层，提高壁垒，让自己变得不可替代。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">资本主义本质是自然选择。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">组织会变小，效率会提高，个体能力会被放大。短期会阵痛，长期是结构性重组。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 129, 36);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">真正的问题从来不是“AI会不会替代我”，而是“我会不会利用AI让自己升级”。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">历史不会等人，它只奖励顺应趋势的人。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">这一次，我们正在见证新的分水岭。</span></p></section></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 24px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: unset;font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: right;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">文案：凯莉</span></span></p><p style="text-align: right;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">版面：紫雯</span></span></p></section></section><section style="display: flex;flex-flow: row;text-align: center;justify-content: center;margin: 10px 0% 4px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 0 0 0%;height: auto;align-self: flex-start;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 6px;height: 6px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(0, 47, 167);box-sizing: border-box;"><svg viewBox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;" role="img" aria-label="插图"></svg></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 0 0 0%;height: auto;align-self: flex-start;margin: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 6px;height: 6px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(0, 47, 167);box-sizing: border-box;"><svg viewBox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;" role="img" aria-label="插图"></svg></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 0 0 0%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 6px;height: 6px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(0, 47, 167);box-sizing: border-box;"><svg viewBox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;" role="img" aria-label="插图"></svg></section></section></section></section><section style="line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: center;"><section><s